Package: BayesLatReg
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Latent Generalized Linear Regression with EM
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Cheung Cheuk Hin Alvin
Maintainer: Cheung Cheuk Hin Alvin <alvin.cheung@example.com>
Description: Fits multivariate Bayesian Latent Linear and Generalized Linear 
    Regression models. Uses a Quasi-Newton Expectation-Maximization (EM) 
    algorithm to partition observations into hidden classes, performing 
    simultaneous estimation and variance contraction profiling.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
